lead_paragraph: The Belmont Stakes winner Jazil will not run in the Breeders’ Cup Classic at Churchill Downs next month. His handlers have set next year’s Dubai World Cup as their next goal. Jazil recently recovered from a bruised bone in his right hind leg.
